trans-unit.source: Defines the lock that implements single-writer/multiple-reader semantics.
trans-unit.target: Define o bloqueio que implementa a semântica de único gravador/vários leitores.

trans-unit.source: This is a value type.
trans-unit.target: Este é um tipo de valor.

trans-unit.source: The following example shows how to request a reader lock, upgrade the reader lock to a writer lock, and save the <xref:System.Threading.LockCookie>.
trans-unit.target: O exemplo a seguir mostra como solicitar um bloqueio de leitor, atualize o bloqueio de leitor para um bloqueio de gravador e salvar o <xref:System.Threading.LockCookie>.

trans-unit.source: It then uses the <xref:System.Threading.LockCookie> to downgrade to a reader lock again.
trans-unit.target: Ele usa o <xref:System.Threading.LockCookie> para fazer o downgrade para um bloqueio de leitor novamente.

trans-unit.source: This code is part of a larger example provided for the <xref:System.Threading.ReaderWriterLock> class.
trans-unit.target: Esse código é parte de um exemplo maior fornecido para a <xref:System.Threading.ReaderWriterLock> classe.

trans-unit.source: This type is thread safe.
trans-unit.target: Este tipo é thread-safe.

trans-unit.source: Indicates whether the current is equal to a specified object.
trans-unit.target: Indica se o objeto atual é igual a um objeto especificado.

trans-unit.source: The object to compare to the current instance.
trans-unit.target: O objeto a ser comparado com a instância atual.

trans-unit.source: Indicates whether a specified object is a <see cref="T:System.Threading.LockCookie" /> and is equal to the current instance.
trans-unit.target: Indica se o objeto especificado é um <see cref="T:System.Threading.LockCookie" /> e é igual à instância atual.

trans-unit.source: <see langword="true" /> if the value of <paramref name="obj" /> is equal to the value of the current instance; otherwise, <see langword="false" />.
trans-unit.target: <see langword="true" /> se o valor de <paramref name="obj" /> for igual ao valor da instância atual; caso contrário, <see langword="false" />.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.Threading.LockCookie" /> to compare to the current instance.
trans-unit.target: O <see cref="T:System.Threading.LockCookie" /> a ser comparado com a instância atual.

trans-unit.source: Indicates whether the current instance is equal to the specified <see cref="T:System.Threading.LockCookie" />.
trans-unit.target: Indica se a instância atual é igual ao <see cref="T:System.Threading.LockCookie" /> especificado.

trans-unit.source: <see langword="true" /> if <paramref name="obj" /> is equal to the value of the current instance; otherwise, <see langword="false" />.
trans-unit.target: <see langword="true" /> se <paramref name="obj" /> é igual ao valor da instância atual; caso contrário, <see langword="false" />.

trans-unit.source: Returns the hash code for this instance.
trans-unit.target: Retorna o código hash para essa instância.

trans-unit.source: A 32-bit signed integer hash code.
trans-unit.target: Um código de hash do inteiro assinado de 32 bits.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.Threading.LockCookie" /> to compare to <c>b</c>.
trans-unit.target: O <see cref="T:System.Threading.LockCookie" /> a ser comparado com <c>b</c>.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.Threading.LockCookie" /> to compare to <c>a</c>.
trans-unit.target: O <see cref="T:System.Threading.LockCookie" /> a ser comparado com <c>a</c>.

trans-unit.source: Indicates whether two <see cref="T:System.Threading.LockCookie" /> structures are equal.
trans-unit.target: Indica se duas estruturas <see cref="T:System.Threading.LockCookie" /> são iguais.

trans-unit.source: <see langword="true" /> if <paramref name="a" /> is equal to <paramref name="b" />; otherwise, <see langword="false" />.
trans-unit.target: <see langword="true" /> se <paramref name="a" /> for igual a <paramref name="b" />; caso contrário, <see langword="false" />.

trans-unit.source: The equivalent method for this operator is <xref:System.Threading.LockCookie.Equals%28System.Threading.LockCookie%29?displayProperty=nameWithType>.
trans-unit.target: O método equivalente para esse operador é <xref:System.Threading.LockCookie.Equals%28System.Threading.LockCookie%29?displayProperty=nameWithType>.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.Threading.LockCookie" /> to compare to <c>b</c>.
trans-unit.target: O <see cref="T:System.Threading.LockCookie" /> a ser comparado com <c>b</c>.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.Threading.LockCookie" /> to compare to <c>a</c>.
trans-unit.target: O <see cref="T:System.Threading.LockCookie" /> a ser comparado com <c>a</c>.

trans-unit.source: Indicates whether two <see cref="T:System.Threading.LockCookie" /> structures are not equal.
trans-unit.target: Indica se duas estruturas <see cref="T:System.Threading.LockCookie" /> não são iguais.

trans-unit.source: <see langword="true" /> if <paramref name="a" /> is not equal to <paramref name="b" />; otherwise, <see langword="false" />.
trans-unit.target: <see langword="true" /> se <paramref name="a" /> não for igual a <paramref name="b" />; caso contrário, <see langword="false" />.

trans-unit.source: The equivalent method for this operator is <xref:System.Threading.LockCookie.Equals%28System.Threading.LockCookie%29?displayProperty=nameWithType>.
